{"tid":565561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係有咁多有錢佬？識幾個港女好似求其都識到有錢人","createTime":"2018-02-19T05:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T06:36:10.000Z","uid":124114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1c419bbbadf078ebbe74a205ee89251dd1a67191","tid":565561,"uid":124114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:54:12.000Z","msg":"有冇咁多荀盤？仲要佢地唔靚<br />\n有個同ibank佬行緊，一個同緊機師，一個同上市公司二世祖<br />\n但係呢幾條女真係好普通，唔知點識返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6384247e61a3fac75c3cf970e70bec04ac975065","tid":565561,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:02:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cec5999305859b6655d0586e0c1a7d571219e78d","tid":565561,"uid":172278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"巴打 知唔知香港堅尼係數有幾高？<br />\n係香港一係有錢，一係好窮<br />\n仲有臭閪主義抬頭，一般正常既女 都變女神<br />\n所以有閪就好易識都有錢佬"},{"pid":"f6900becb88de90cf405693f3a139dec760f05bd","tid":565561,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"有錢佬成日叫雞？"},{"pid":"ca3e0dc740f90901bfc415638e5e93a11945f09e","tid":565561,"uid":150457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"其實識埋堆就得，唔洗好多心計，當然要本身靚<br />\n<br />\n試過番啲財經pr，有個女同事好鬼靚<br />\n我地就要做媒去press com嘅，扮下記者問問題<br />\n<br />\n完場，即刻有幾個男仔埋去交換卡片，一個係間公司大股東黎<br />\n其他都好高富帥feel，即係天生贏家黎<br />\n<br />\n所以本身高質靚女，唔講做野咁簡單，tinder，cb都識大把有錢仔啦<br />\n事實上香港地都真係大把有錢人<br />\n一入到個圈子，就真係求其指一個，都係貝沙灣住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53cc6d2a5ea27f8b718cff92fbe7a07455a977b","tid":565561,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:34:23.000Z","msg":"香港大把有錢人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788b06b7dad28a483f25